bio.openEndedText:
With a lifelong passion for cars, games, and sports, I bring a diverse blend of experiences to the world of car sharing. As a former professional gamer in StarCraft: Brood War and Counter-Strike, my skills in communication and teamwork now fuel my commitment to providing an exceptional car sharing experience.

Outside of gaming and cars, my life is brightened by the presence of Bella, my delightful half Labrador, half Golden Retriever companion. Although Bella is a major part of my life, I ensure she never accompanies me in any of my Turo vehicles to maintain the highest standards of cleanliness.

Having originated from a strong customer service background and currently immersed in the gaming industry, I began hosting on Turo in September 2023. This role has been a joyful extension of my career, allowing me to meet wonderful new people and deliver first-rate service with every interaction. My goal is to enhance your experience and make every trip memorable.

Whether you’re planning a road trip, need a car for commuting, or simply want to explore the great sights of California, consider me your go-to for a fun and seamless adventure in the vibrant San Francisco Bay Area!

In my fleet, every vehicle isn’t just a rental; it's a car I would personally drive. This philosophy ensures that each car meets a high standard of quality and reliability. I take no shortcuts when it comes to maintenance and service—all work is carried out at authorized dealerships or by a trusted mechanic to guarantee that everything is up to par. I do this not just to meet expectations, but to exceed them, ensuring that all my vehicles are safe, reliable, and ready to enhance your journey. When you choose one of my cars, you're not just renting a vehicle—you're gaining peace of mind for your travels.
